{"arkId":"cl010114146","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010114146","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale astronomique \u00e0 cadran solaire","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale astronomique \u00e0 cadran solaire"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1615","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1615,"imprecision":"","text":"D\u00e9but du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Ballard","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6219","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ovale orn\u00e9e d\u0027\u00e9maux champlev\u00e9s, polychromes et translucides ; le bo\u00eetier figure sur son fond, ouvrant \u00e0 charni\u00e8re, une all\u00e9gorie de l\u0027Abondance au milieu de grotesques ; sur sa carrure, des sc\u00e8nes de chasse au cerf et au sanglier. Int\u00e9rieur contenant un cadran solaire avec boussole. Couvercle du cadran muni d\u0027un cristal de roche serti de griffes. Pendant en forme de chapiteau ; \u00e0 l\u0027oppos\u00e9, bouton moulur\u00e9. Plaque du cadran grav\u00e9e de rinceaux fleuris peupl\u00e9s de figurines fantastiques. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains (heures), arabes (\u00e2ges de la lune) inscrits sur un anneau dont le centre est d\u00e9cor\u00e9 d\u0027un lambrequin et d\u0027une couronne feuillag\u00e9e translucides ; mois apparaissant dans un guichet. Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet ajour\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux \u00e0 fleurs de fraisier.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : J Ballard\/Bourges","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7,9","displayDimension":"7,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,9","displayDimension":"2,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Bourges (Centre-\u003ECher)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jean-Charles Seguin (1857-1908), Paris ; legs Seguin, 1908 ; cf. AN 20144787\/16, 1909 28 ao\u00fbt : \u002240. montre XVIe argent ovale\t\t - 5000 francs\u0022","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Seguin, Jean-Charles","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1908","startYear":1908,"endYear":1908}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610